description.displayText: Jazmine has been an amazing nanny to our children. Jazmine worked for us for 1.5 years and took great care of our kids (infant twins and a two year old). The kids love her and she took care of them as if they were her own children. We've brought Jazmine on trips with us and consider her a member of the family. My husband and I both work and Jazmine was always on time and dependable. The only reason we parted ways is because the twins are enrolling in preschool. We love Jazmine!
